kṛṣṇācalas tu tadā samāpattiṃ tyaktvā śvetācalādivatmaṇḍaleyo bhavati | dveṣavajrī tu mohavajryādisthāne bhavatīti bhāvaḥ ||

<commentary>pañcayogīti svābhilāṣataḥ | svadehavarṇato vā | pūrvaseveti | maṇḍalāt pūrvaṃ bhagavadbhāvanāpūrvakaṃ lakṣam ekaṃ oṃ caṇḍamahāroṣaṇa hūṃ phaṭ ity asya japtvā maṇḍalaṃ kuryāt | etena sarvavighnopaśamanaṃ bhavatīty arthaḥ ||</commentary>

madyetyādi | madajanakaṃ surāmaireyādibhedabhinnaṃ jaladravyaṃ madyaṃ |
